One-shot chat REPL without launching the full TUI (GaussClaw extension)

Usage: chat [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -m, --message <TEXT>
          Send a single message and exit (non-interactive mode)

  -s, --session <ID>
          Use a specific session ID instead of starting a new one

  -h, --help
          Print help
